headline: Energy Royalty Company Texas Pacific Land Corp (TPL) Surges After AI Pivot
summary: Texas Pacific Land Corporation (NYSE:TPL) has surged 44% year-to-date through February 11. The stock trades at $413.54, up from $287.22 at 2025 year-end. Shares climbed 31.6% over the past month and 17.8% in the last week. Most incredibly, out of 500 stocks in the S&P 500, Texas Pacific Land Corp has the 8th-best returns year-to-date. ...
